@@ -0,0 +1,19 @@
+Gabriel Services language toggle fix summary
+
+Files updated:
+- index.html
+- en/index.html
+- es/index.html
+- assets/language-switcher.js
+- assets/legal-i18n.js
+- styles.css
+
+What changed:
+1. Homepage EN/ES controls were changed from JavaScript-only buttons to real anchor links.
+2. The language switcher now prefers each control's explicit href/data-lang-href instead of guessing the destination path.
+3. Legal page i18n switching was hardened with the same explicit-target behavior.
+4. Lang toggle styling now guarantees visible click affordance for anchors and buttons.
+
+Result:
+- EN and ES toggles now have direct destinations even if JavaScript is delayed or partially fails.
+- When JavaScript is active, the switcher still updates localStorage, aria states, and navigates to the correct localized page.
diff -ruN /tmp/gabo_orig/gaboservices-main/assets/language-switcher.js gaboservices-main/assets/language-switcher.js
